headline: Chase the Rebound in Toll Brothers (TOL) Stock?
summary: As a leading luxury homebuilder, Toll Brothers (TOL) stock has seen a sharp rebound with the company benefiting from a more affluent customer base that's less sensitive to interest rates.

headline: Hovnanian (HOV) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Miss Estimates
summary: Hovnanian (HOV) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -43.30% and -0.70%, respectively, for the quarter ended July 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Lennar Introduces Shearwater, Offering Rear-Entry Garage Townhomes in St. Augustine
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, today announced the grand opening of brand-new model townhomes in the latest phase of Shearwater, a premier master-planned community in St. Johns county. The models feature stylish rear-entry garages, a new and unique product offering designed to enhance walkability, front-street appeal, and community connectivity.
